race.comment: TYPHOON BAYLEE (1) comes off a slick 25.15 placing at Ballarat over 450m. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. LISSY'S A DEMON (7) scored by 3.5 lengths last time (23.32) in a Grade 5 over 410m at Horsham. Already a winner from this draw. PAW FABIAN (4) is racing consistently without winning, finishing in the minors three on end. Last start flew out of the boxes but gathered in and finished third (29.55) at Sandown. Include. Something for the Multiples: DEROGATIVE (5)
